{"tid":2284333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：理解美國總統需時確定 但失去美國軍工影響力 需祝賀拜登借東風","createTime":"2020-11-13T08:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T08:39:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7205d1efe04ff1147f603792a330e0bf9fd8c7ca","tid":2284333,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"外交部：中方尊重美國人民選擇 向拜登表示祝賀<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部向宣布勝出美國總統大選的拜登表示祝賀。<br />\n<br />\n發言人汪文斌在例行記者會表示，中方一直關注美國國內和國際社會對美國總統選舉的反應，中方尊重美國人民的選擇，向拜登和賀錦麗表示祝賀，同時理解美國大選的結果會按照美國的法律和程序作出確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559857-20201113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559857-20201113.htm&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=52f218b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559857-20201113.htm&h=13236b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559857-20201113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11ae0c7d3aed120a49ef00df7ed73f1ed088395f","tid":2284333,"uid":164374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"中方尊重美國人民的選擇, 一個淨係專重外國人民選擇既政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81516ac2ba1c2d3083575d8eddb95fad25ff2509","tid":2284333,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f81ab715f3219d76e57db91bff00b953bcdeb3f","tid":2284333,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"俄大哥都未出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf357b1cbea77d92cd5e0a86bf68e57f807a52dd","tid":2284333,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20